# 🍽 Restaurant Discovery Website

A responsive frontend web application that displays real-time restaurant data using an external API.  
Built to practice API integration, filtering logic, and modular UI architecture.

## 🚀 Features

- 🔍 Search restaurants by name
- ⭐ Filter restaurants based on ratings
- 🍜 Filter by cuisines
- ⚡ Real-time data fetching from external API
- 📱 Fully responsive design


## 🛠 Tech Stack

- React.js
- JavaScript (ES6+)
- HTML5
- CSS3
- REST API Integration

## 🧠 What I Learned

- Handling asynchronous API calls using fetch / async-await
- Managing loading and error states
- Component-based architecture in React
- Implementing dynamic filtering logic
- Writing clean and reusable UI components

## 📂 Project Structure

- Components-based modular structure
- API service handling
- Reusable restaurant card component
- Search & filter functionality
